    "The term (c S0 + v A0) is the sum of the sound speed and the Alfvén speed computed from the initial MHS atmosphere.",
    "The coefficients c const (u) are the amplitudes of the diffusivity of different primary variables u = [ρ 1, ρv, e 1, B 1 ].",
